 :tx/rationale "Create task: RDI-TEST: Comprehensive verification for Resolution-Deliberation Isomorphism — 3 layers: algebraic proptest + integration test + E2E script. BACKGROUND: INV-RESOLUTION-009 requires 3 verification layers. Layer 1 (algebraic): proptest that for any ResolutionRecord R, resolution_to_decision(R) produces a Decision D where D.method matches R.mode AND D.positions.len() == R.competing_values.len() AND D.outcome == R.winner. This is the isomorphism correctness check — the functor preserves structure. Layer 2 (integration): create store, cause conflict (two agents assert different values for same entity+attribute), run merge + cascade, verify BOTH :resolution/* entity AND :deliberation/decision entity are produced for the same conflict, linked by :resolution/decision Ref. Layer 3 (E2E): scripts/e2e_resolution_precedent.sh — full pipeline: init, create conflict, resolve, verify precedent query returns the decision, create second conflict on same attribute, verify precedent count=2, simulate override, verify escalation signal. 15+ checks. FBW integration test: create FBW binding to a Decision entity from a resolution, verify staleness detection when the resolution is later overridden. ACCEPTANCE: (A) Proptest: isomorphism preserves structure for arbitrary ResolutionRecords. (B) Integration: merge produces linked Resolution+Decision entities. (C) E2E: 15+ checks all pass. (D) FBW: witness goes stale on resolution override. DEPENDS-ON: RDI-4. FILE: crates/braid-kernel/src/resolution.rs (tests) + scripts/e2e_resolution_precedent.sh"
